By providing my bank account or credit card account information to Green Mountain Energy Company and checking the box provided, I hereby authorize Green Mountain Energy Company to charge my account in the amount due of my monthly invoice on an ongoing basis. I understand that debits to my checking account will be made on the due date appearing on my invoice, unless such date is Saturday, Sunday, or other bank holiday, in which case Green Mountain will debit my account on the next banking day. I understand that my monthly Green Mountain Energy® invoice, together with this authorization, will be notice of the amount and date of each withdrawal from my bank account. I also agree to notify Green Mountain Energy Company if there are any changes to my bank account or credit card account information. I understand that my information will remain strictly confidential per the privacy policy of Green Mountain Energy Company. I understand that I will continue to receive a copy of my monthly electricity bill for my records, but my bill will be marked "Do Not Pay."  





													
